trailer.title: Money Heist
trailer.videoDescription: Lives are on the line as the Professor's plan begins to unravel and the crew must fend off enemies from both inside and outside the Bank of Spain.

similars.title: Stranger Things
similars.plot: When a young boy disappears, his mother, a police chief and his friends must confront terrifying supernatural forces in order to get him back.
similars.stars: Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Winona Ryder

similars.title: Peaky Blinders
similars.plot: A gangster family epic set in 1900s England, centering on a gang who sew razor blades in the peaks of their caps, and their fierce boss Tommy Shelby.
similars.stars: Cillian Murphy, Paul Anderson, Helen McCrory

similars.title: Elite
similars.plot: When three working-class teenagers begin attending an exclusive private school in Spain, the clash between them and the wealthy students leads to murder.
similars.stars: Miguel Bernardeau, Arón Piper, Itzan Escamilla

similars.title: Breaking Bad
similars.plot: A high school chemistry teacher diagnosed with inoperable lung cancer turns to manufacturing and selling methamphetamine in order to secure his family's future.
similars.stars: Bryan Cranston, Aaron Paul, Anna Gunn

similars.title: Dark
similars.plot: A family saga with a supernatural twist, set in a German town, where the disappearance of two young children exposes the relationships among four families.
similars.stars: Louis Hofmann, Karoline Eichhorn, Lisa Vicari

similars.title: Lucifer
similars.plot: Lucifer Morningstar has decided he's had enough of being the dutiful servant in Hell and decides to spend some time on Earth to better understand humanity. He settles in Los Angeles - the City of Angels.
similars.stars: Tom Ellis, Lauren German, Kevin Alejandro

similars.title: Game of Thrones
similars.plot: Nine noble families fight for control over the lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.
similars.stars: Emilia Clarke, Peter Dinklage, Kit Harington

similars.title: Prison Break
similars.plot: Due to a political conspiracy, an innocent man is sent to death row and his only hope is his brother, who makes it his mission to deliberately get himself sent to the same prison in order to break the both of them out, from the inside.
similars.stars: Dominic Purcell, Wentworth Miller, Amaury Nolasco

similars.title: Vikings
similars.plot: Vikings transports us to the brutal and mysterious world of Ragnar Lothbrok, a Viking warrior and farmer who yearns to explore - and raid - the distant shores across the ocean.
similars.stars: Katheryn Winnick, Gustaf Skarsgård, Alexander Ludwig

similars.title: Money Heist: The Phenomenon
similars.plot: A documentary on why and how "Money Heist" sparked a wave of enthusiasm around the world for a lovable group of thieves and their professor.

similars.title: Sherlock
similars.plot: A modern update finds the famous sleuth and his doctor partner solving crime in 21st century London.
similars.stars: Benedict Cumberbatch, Martin Freeman, Una Stubbs

similars.title: The Witcher
similars.plot: Geralt of Rivia, a solitary monster hunter, struggles to find his place in a world where people often prove more wicked than beasts.
similars.stars: Anna Shaffer, Henry Cavill, Freya Allan
